text: Femke Markus (born 17 November 1996) is a Dutch professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . She is a younger sister of Riejanne Markus, but they are not related to Barry Markus and his sister Kelly Markus. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
